snippet.title: Marvel's Women of Power - Launch Trailer | PS4, PS3, PS Vita
snippet.description:
Marvel’s Women of Power two-pack combines two tables that feature the mightiest female Super Heroes and Super Villians in the Marvel Universe! Wage an epic battle alongside Black Widow and Madam Masque in an alternate Soviet-dominated reality on the A-Force table, and defeat Bombshell with Ms. Marvel, Squirrel Girl, Spider-Gwen and more on the exciting Champions table!

http://www.marvelpinball.com

Marvel's Women of Power is available now for Zen Pinball 2 on PlayStation 4, PlayStation 3, and PlayStation Vita!
